::Epyon::

"They probably checled our course and droped persuit."
He continued to fly to the CF. He was less the 5 miles out now.

::Hot Rod::

After having a few energon drinks, he walked outside. He saw the War
Machines, and went up to them.
"What are you bots doing here?"

::Demolition::

He waited for Havoc to answer Hot Rod, since he was commander.

::DrillBit::

He quickly transformed to beast mode, and drilled away from Depth
Charge, at fast speeds. He opened a comm.
"Killfest, DarkFate, I'm pulling out. Where are you two and what do we
do now?"

::Dollon::

Fed up with the no show traders, he gets back into the shuttle and takes
off for the Black Fortress.
